// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1156 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: d98f9cf5-cee1-5bbf-aec3-e825ccf06105

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:10* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:18.04-ESM* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:22.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
